Gerard Pique celebrated Barcelona's 2-0 win over Rayo Vallecano by going mushroom picking with Shakira.

The South American star posted a photo on her Instagram account of the two of them picking mushrooms with friends. 

The 37-year-old singer wrote: 'Día de setas,' or 'Mushroom day.' 

